A: You can use the following code to generate the signature in Java:
public static String generateSignature(String secret, String pathAndQuery) {
    try {
        MessageDigest md = MessageDigest.getInstance("SHA-256");
        md.update(secret.getBytes("UTF-8"));
        md.update(pathAndQuery.getBytes("UTF-8"));
        byte[] digest = md.digest();
        return Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(digest);
    } catch (Exception e) {
        e.printStackTrace();
    }
    return null;
}
